il url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_04/now_staytuned_album_rollouts_260430-ytfzxi.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 17:42:59 GMT</pubDate><title>The evolution of album rollouts</title><updateDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 17:47:40 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Marlene Lenthang</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Sun, 10 May 2026 19:44:48 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Savannah Guthrie has shared a heart-wrenching Mother’s Day post, pleading for the public’s help in locating her missing mother saying “We need help.”The “TODAY” show co-anchor shared a video compilation on her Instagram Sunday sharing sweet moments with her mother, Nancy Guthrie.“Mother, daughter, sister, Nonie — we miss you with every breath.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/savannah-guthrie-shares-heartwrenching-mothers-day-post-rcna344437</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/savannah-guthrie-shares-heartwrenching-mothers-day-post-rcna344437</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-02/260214-nancy-guthrie-memorial-ribbons-ww-1814-91f8ed.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Diannie Chavez</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Two yellow ribbons are tied around neighboring trees along a gravel road in a desert landscape.</media:text><media:description type="plain">Yellow ribbons tied in a bow, a gesture of support for Nancy Guthrie and her family, near Guthrie&#39;s home in the Catalina Foothills development in Tucson, Ariz. in February.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-02/260214-nancy-guthrie-memorial-ribbons-ww-1814-91f8ed.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 19:44:48 GMT</pubDate><title>‘We will never stop looking for you’: Savannah Guthrie shares heart-wrenching Mother’s Day post</title><updateDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 19:44:48 GMT</updateDate></item></channel></rss>